/* Oshihandithwa shi tar oshi shi ningile ko ndjila ya ndjila oyo ya pewa. Oku shi ningwa oku li nawa, galula oshiti; ohandi, sho oshike shoka osha ningwa oshihandithwa shi ningile (ngoka: oshihandithwa oshi li po, oshihandithwa shi li ngele, inashi ningwa oshihandithwa shi ningile), galula oshiti.

